<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About – MediConnect</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
  <div class="page-container">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>About MediConnect</h1>
      <p>Simplifying healthcare access for everyone in India.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>🎯 Our Mission</h2>
        <p>MediConnect bridges the gap between patients and healthcare providers by offering a seamless appointment booking experience and secure access to medical records — all from the comfort of home.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>🩺 For Doctors</h2>
        <p>Doctors can log in with their dedicated credentials to view patient appointments, update statuses, and upload medical reports — making follow-ups and record-sharing effortless.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>👤 For Patients</h2>
        <p>Patients can register, book appointments with verified specialists, and securely view all reports uploaded by their doctors — keeping their health records in one place.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
